# This project stores secrets in the macOS Keychain, NOT in a .env file.
# There is nothing you need to put here — this file only documents the two
# Keychain items the app reads. Set them once with `security` (see README).
#
#   Telegram bot token (from @BotFather):
#     security add-generic-password -s claude-tg-bridge -a bot -w '<TOKEN>'
#
# Optional runtime overrides (rarely needed) can be set as real env vars:
#   NONE required for normal use.
